{"tid":2383883,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後第二個星期","createTime":"2021-01-28T08:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T15:41:13.000Z","uid":209418,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7eddff5370f734def38c893f0a526b7bf98d413","tid":2383883,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"令我有感而發唱咗首P.S I Love You<br />\n<br />\n雖然一切都完咗，但我會好好咁活下去<br />\n<br />\n唔再尋死。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你為我上咗人生入面最重要嘅一課<br />\n<br />\n再見了，過去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2tw_YeSHs3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2tw_YeSHs3g&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ab826be6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2tw_YeSHs3g</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唱得唔係好好，但起碼我將內心嘅嘢都表達哂喺歌詞度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d886a5bb0791da589a3cc08dc43a14f027c05c26","tid":2383883,"uid":372094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f57e110ffbd81364d0642b98150560f8ab5824","tid":2383883,"uid":209418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d886a5bb0791da589a3cc08dc43a14f027c05c26","tid":2383883,"uid":372094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"感情台嘅清同絲某程度上真係幫咗我好多<br />\n<br />\n我好感激佢哋對我嘅每一個留言<br />\n<br />\n現實入面我冇辦法搵到舒壓自己情緒嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n但喺感情台我可以同世界任何人都暢所欲言<br />\n<br />\n多謝你哋屌醒我同安慰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d390b93fb2d6cd25952203c6ecba04ef25630a","tid":2383883,"uid":372094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1f57e110ffbd81364d0642b98150560f8ab5824","tid":2383883,"uid":209418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d886a5bb0791da589a3cc08dc43a14f027c05c26"